EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
DNC 19.
DISTRESS SIGNAL RECEIVED ON 406 MHZ FROM AIRCRAFT
IN AREA WITHIN 15 MILES OF 53-30N 016-15W
AT 121407Z NOV. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO
KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
REPORTS TO UK COAST GUARD, PHONE: 4434 4382 0025,
E-MAIL: UKMRCC@HMCG.GOV.UK.
